Title: Supply the Effort
Description:
When shadow fell upon our town, many necessary supplies were taken in the cover of darkness.

With the light returning, it is time to rebuild, but first, we must retrieve what was lost. 

Search the surrounding areas, recover any supplies that might be useful. Then, deliver them to Ceren Leadland.
ObjectivesText: Recover various stolen items from the surrounding area to satisfy our needs.
RewardText: You have recovered far more than we could have hoped.  I've set some of the extras aside for you to have.

Objectives.Text: Recover any supplies you can find
